---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import practiceData from '../../data/practices.json';
import { url } from '../../utils/url';
---

<PageLayout title="Complaints procedure" description="Procedure for submitting complaints at Schoterpoort General Practice" lang="en">
  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <article class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none prose-headings:text-neutral-900 prose-a:text-dark-600 prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline">
        <h1>Complaints procedure</h1>

        <p>Most patients are satisfied with the care provided. If you do have a complaint or concern, you are encouraged to discuss it with your GP first and work towards a solution together.</p>

        <p>This also applies to complaints about a practice assistant, practice nurse, mental health practitioner, or practice organisation. Once the GP is aware of your concerns, a solution can often be found together.</p>

        <p>The practice takes complaints seriously -- first and foremost for you personally, but also because they can contribute to improving the quality of our practice.</p>

        <h2>Submitting a complaint</h2>

        <p>When you submit a complaint via ZIVVER the complaints coordinator will ensure it is processed within the practice. You will receive confirmation of receipt and be contacted about the most appropriate next steps -- for example a conversation with the GP or staff member concerned.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- ZIVVER landing card -->
      <div class="not-prose bg-primary-50 rounded-xl border-2 border-primary-200 p-8 text-center mt-6 mb-12">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Submit a complaint securely via ZIVVER</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-6">Your complaint is sent securely to the practice's complaints officer.</p>

        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-left">
          <div class="bg-accent-50 border-l-4 border-accent-400 rounded-r-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-accent-800 font-semibold">This is not intended for medical emergencies. In an emergency, call your GP directly or, outside office hours, the Emergency Service (<a href={`tel:${practiceData.phoneEmergency.replace(/[\s-]/g, '')}`} class="underline">{practiceData.phoneEmergency}</a>).</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://app.zivver.com/l/start/de82dba5-f8cf-4001-b23b-6378c09368f0"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-dark-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl no-underline hover:bg-dark-800 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" />
          </svg>
          Submit complaint via ZIVVER
        </a>

        <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-primary-200 text-left text-sm text-neutral-600">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-700 mb-2 text-center">Unable to use ZIVVER?</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mb-3 text-center">Call the practice during office hours ({practiceData.openingstijden.daysShortEn} {practiceData.openingstijden.open} -- {practiceData.openingstijden.close}):</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1">
            {practiceData.practices.map((practice) => (
              <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-xs">{practice.name}</span>
                <a href={`tel:${practice.phone.replace(/\s/g, '')}`} class="text-dark-700 font-medium no-underline text-xs">{practice.phone}</a>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <article class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none prose-headings:text-neutral-900 prose-a:text-dark-600 prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline">
        <h2>External complaints handling</h2>

        <p>If you do not wish to proceed internally, or we cannot resolve the issue together, you can contact an independent complaints officer at DOkH (complaints and disputes department).</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Address:</strong> Robijnstraat 6, 1812 RB Alkmaar</li>
          <li><strong>Telephone:</strong> 072-5208325</li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:klachtenengeschillen@dokh.nl">klachtenengeschillen@dokh.nl</a></li>
          <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://www.dokh.nl">www.dokh.nl</a></li>
        </ul>

        <p>The practice is also affiliated with the DOkH disputes committee.</p>

        <h2>Complaints regulations</h2>

        <p>The procedure of our internal complaints handling is set out in a regulation so you know exactly where you stand.</p>

        <p><a href={url('/documents/klachtenreglement.pdf')}>Complaints regulations Schoterpoort Huisartsenpraktijk</a></p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
